title: Claire Ryann and her dad make adorable music videos together. Singing
text:
Claire Ryann and her dad make adorable music videos together. Singing a live duet with her dad, little Claire is seen singing Randy Newman’s ‘You’ve got a friend in me’ from the movie ‘Toy Story’. Her expressions and her melodious voice will surely win your heart.
And just when you think she floors us all with her amazing singing skills, take a look at how adorably Claire announces the song which she is gonna sing.
You can check out other music videos of Claire and Dad on their Youtube channel Claire and the Crosbys . But as of now happy listening to this one!
